# General Media Preparation

## Purpose

Students should be able to:

1. Understand that microbes must have a food source for growth.
2. Make nutrient broth tubes.
3. Make nutrient agar slants.
4. Make nutrient agar plates.

## Video Tutorials

1. [Preparing nutrient broth and agar](https://youtu.be/VhynEsEPWF0)
2. [Pouring agar plates](https://youtu.be/X4L16Vu5MSk)
3. Transfering nutrient broth to test tubes
4. Making nutrient agar slants

